LAGOS  – SMARTMARK Limited has explained why it brought the Charles Tyrwhitt brand to the Nigerian market. Mr. John Onyeoguzoro, the Chief Executive Officer of the company, said that Charles Tyr­whitt makes it easy for men to look effortlessly sharp with its various product categories such as shirts, suits, shoes, chi­nos, ties, cufflinks, knitwear, pocket squares, socks, belts, underwear and loungewear. He stated that Charles Tyr­whitt made the iconic Jermyn Street shirt accessible to men around the world and has since built up a full men’s wardrobe offer, along with the style and the confidence of millions of loyal customers. The Chief Executive Offi­cer of SMARTMARK stated that Charles Tyrwhitt focus is on making it easy for men to dress well. According to him, SMART­MARK brands include Swatch, T M Lewin, Charles Tyrwhitt, Levi’s, Dune, Aldo, Tommy Hil­figer, Mother care and a multi-brand sports store, Fast foward and others. He added that some of the brands in the Fast for ward multi-brand store include brands like Nike, Adidas, Rebook, New Bal­ance, Converse, BLK, etc. He disclosed that t SMART­MARK has over 60 stores in West Africa, adding that people who are interested in its ecom­merce space should visit www. ffstoes.com. He stated that the advantage is that it is an Omni channel platform where online custom­ers can select their products, pay up conveniently across the brick and mortar or get delivery within 24 hours in the comfort of their offices and homes. -Advertisement- POLL He  revealed that all purchases made through the e-commerce platform attract special dis­counts and loyalty deals, adding that SMARTMARK Limited and Charles Tyrwhitt were ex­cited to launch the famous pre­mium brand (Charles Tyrwhitt) in Nigeria at lkeja City Mall.